{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"fed4137369","title":"四川省交通厅分配新进人员的通知","origin":"根据文件翻印件打印。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"0c2f9edc46","index":0,"year":1958,"month":9,"day":13,"articleId":"fed4137369"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"f13324661c","type":"title","text":"四川省交通厅分配新进人员的通知","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"fed4137369"},{"id":"8a2483bf3f","type":"appellation","text":"公路局、公路设计院、重庆运输公司、重庆、成都、橡胶厂、重庆、成都、泸州、雅安、交通机械厂：","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"fed4137369"},{"id":"4bc16281c4","type":"paragraph","text":"目前有一批未考取高等学校的高中毕业生，由国家统一分配工作。现已由省分配给我厅部份，根据我厅具体情况，经研究决定，分配厅属各单位。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"fed4137369"},{"id":"5bbff95187","type":"paragraph","text":"该批学生，人很年轻，成绩一般还好；但多系家庭成份不好，社会关系复杂，或整风运动中有比较严重的右派言论。为此，决定该批人员一律作试用干部。并只宜作一般行政业务或会计工作，不能安置作机要工作，并希今后多加强政治教育。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"fed4137369"},{"id":"07e4da738b","type":"paragraph","text":"试用期间的工资待遇，暂按学生待遇，第一年每人每月13元，第二年15元，第三年17元的规定办理。待上级另文规定后，再行通知。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"fed4137369"},{"id":"8dafeb21a5","type":"paragraph","text":"该批学生前来的旅费，凭单据报销车船费，其它费用自理，除已分别通知本人于10月15日前来你处报到处，兹随文附档案袋，希遵照。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"fed4137369"},{"id":"3966ffee39","type":"paragraph","text":" 四川省交通厅1958年9月13日","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"fed4137369"},{"id":"281352d2e5","type":"paragraph","text":"注：拟稿：李光国；核稿：秦傅林；签发：王长年、赵理。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"fed4137369"},{"id":"128400301f","type":"paragraph","text":"附分配名单。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"fed4137369"},{"id":"1958d1bf15","type":"paragraph","text":"重庆运输公司：12人","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"fed4137369"}],"page":{"id":"e11109e1ba","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"fed4137369","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}